OL,3,CPrisoner found dead in his cell with
OL,4,Cvape in his hand
OL,6,FAn inmate was found dead in his cell
OL,7,Fwith a vape in his hand just 15 hours
OL,8,Fafter he was transferred there from
OL,9,Fanother prison.
OL,11,FStephen Wallwork, 34, was discovered
OL,12,Fby two nurses on the morning after he
OL,13,Farrived at Forest Bank in Pendlebury,
OL,14,FManchester.
