OL,3,CPrisoner found dead in his cell with
OL,4,Cvape in his hand
OL,6,FA report by the Prisons and Probation
OL,7,FOmbudsman said it was possible he had
OL,8,Fsmuggled synthetic cannabinoids inside
OL,9,Fthe prison but he and his belongings -
OL,10,Fincluding numerous open tubs of
OL,11,Fspices, rice and protein powders - had
OL,12,Fnot been properly searched.
OL,14,FAdrian Usher said staff also did not
OL,15,Fproperly check on his welfare when
OL,16,Fthey first unlocked his cell on the
OL,17,Fmorning of his death.
