OL,3,CPrisoner found dead in his cell with
OL,4,Cvape in his hand
OL,6,FA post-mortem report found that,
OL,7,Falthough he had used synthetic
OL,8,Fcannabinoids there was no certainty
OL,9,Fthat this contributed to his death and
OL,10,Fan inquest recorded an open verdict.
OL,12,FIn his report Mr Usher said the father
OL,13,Fof two was the 15th prisoner at Forest
OL,14,FBank to die since July 2021.
OL,16,FNow the Salford MP Rebecca Long Bailey
OL,17,Fsaid she has deep concerns about the
OL,18,Fprison and is calling for an urgent
OL,19,Freview of conditions.
