OL,6,FMr Wallwork's mother, Kelly Kay, 52,
OL,7,Fsaid she was horrified by the findings
OL,8,Fin the report and was speaking out to
OL,9,Ftry to stop another family going
OL,10,Fthrough what she's been through.
OL,12,F"I just want my son back, but I know
OL,13,Fthat will not happen.," she said. "He
OL,14,Fwas our only child. He was my life. I
OL,15,Fwas 16 when I had him and he was
OL,16,Feverything to me."
