OL,6,FSodexo, which runs Forest Bank, said:
OL,7,F"Following any death in custody, our
OL,8,Fpriority is to implement effective and
OL,9,Fpositive changes in the prison. We
OL,10,Freview all conclusions and
OL,11,Frecommendations made by the Coroner or
OL,12,FPPO with great care, as we continue to
OL,13,Fbuild on the progress made to provide
OL,14,Fa safe and rehabilitative environment
OL,15,Fto all prisoners."
